      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and has been a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. The exterior has some noticeable paint fading on the hood and a few minor dents and scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and wear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but it will likely need a brake service and new tires in the near future. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind some cosmetic and minor mechanical projects.",
